{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"2":"Prayer (Kitab Al-Salat)"},"section_detail":{"2":{"hadithnumber_first":391,"hadithnumber_last":1160,"arabicnumber_first":391,"arabicnumber_last":1160}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1126,"arabicnumber":1126,"text":"حدثنا زهير بن حرب، حدثنا هشيم، اخبرنا يحيى بن سعيد، عن عمرة، عن عايشة، - رضى الله عنها - قالت صلى رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم في حجرته والناس ياتمون به من وراء الحجرة","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (729)"}],"reference":{"book":2,"hadith":737}}]}